DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260417T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260418T010000
SUMMARY:Hamilton Friday Salsa
DESCRIPTION:Language Exchange Toronto - Se Habla English & Spanish\n**SALS
 A SOUL** presents the best Salsa & Bachata social in town at the Opening P
 arty of the Latin Coffee Festival @ The Cotton Factory.\n\nGuests are invi
 ted to arrive as doors open at **7:30 p.m.**\, followed by a **Beginner Sa
 lsa Lesson at 7:45 p.m.**\, perfect for newcomers or anyone looking to war
 m up. The energy rises as the **Latin Dance Party kicks off from 9:00 p.m.
  to 1:00 a.m.**\, featuring a lively mix of primarily salsa and bachata.\n
 \nAdmission is **$20 for the party** or **$25 including the lesson**\, and
  each ticket includes a complimentary drink.\n\nAdvance tickets are also a
 vailable through the event’s ticket link: [https://www.zeffy.com/en-CA/t
 icketing/salsa-soul-friday-apr-17-2026-the-cotton-factory](https://www.zef
 fy.com/en-CA/ticketing/salsa-soul-friday-apr-17-2026-the-cotton-factory)\n
 \nThe venue offers **free on-site and neighbourhood parking**\, along with
  a **cash bar** for guests to enjoy throughout the night. No partner or pr
 ior dance experience is required—everyone is welcome to join the celebra
 tion.\n\nNo partner or experience needed! Join us to practice your dance m
 oves and language skills in a fun\, friendly atmosphere.\n\n**More Informa
 tion:**\nhttps://www.salsasoulproductions.com/\nhttps://www.facebook.com/s
 alsasoulproductions/\nhttps://www.meetup.com/hamilton-salsa-soul-socials-d
 ance-meet-up/events/313932037/\n\nDon’t forget to save me a dance! 💃
 🕺\nHéctor
